					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle"></p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
							By <a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/brian-doyle">Brian Doyle</a></li><li><a href="/issues/443">November 2012</a></li></ul>

		

